  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A creature that fails its Reflex save to avoid this snare is treated as if it was successfully affected by a feint. This counts as you performing the feint for the purposes of Fencing sphere talents that depend on feinting a target. Non-humanoids with an Intelligence score of 1 or 2 get a +4 bonus to Reflex saves against this trap and mindless creatures are still immune. If you possess the Unlikely Feint Fencing sphere talent, reduce the bonus to saves non-humanoids with an Intelligence score of 1 or 2 get to their saves to +2 and mindless creatures are vulnerable to this trap but gain a +4 bonus to their Reflex save.</p>\n",
